   "source": [
    "# Movie Recommender PAD — Etapa M: BGE-Large (GPU)\n",
    "\n",
    "Este notebook executa o pipeline completo com `BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5` em todos os 62.423 filmes do MovieLens ml-25m.  \n",
    "**Requer GPU:** Ativar em *Editar > Configurações do notebook > Acelerador de hardware > T4 GPU*.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Antes de rodar:**  \n",
    "Faça upload da pasta `ml-25m/` para o Google Drive em `Meu Drive/ml-25m/`  \n",
    "(ou ajuste `DATA_DIR` na célula de configuração abaixo)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Verificar GPU disponivel\n",
    "import subprocess\n",
    "result = subprocess.run(['nvidia-smi', '--query-gpu=name,memory.total', '--format=csv,noheader'],\n",
    "                        capture_output=True, text=True)\n",
    "if result.returncode == 0:\n",
    "    print('GPU detectada:', result.stdout.strip())\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print('AVISO: GPU nao detectada. Va em Editar > Configuracoes do notebook > T4 GPU.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Montar Google Drive (onde ficam os dados ml-25m e o cache de embeddings)\n",
    "from google.colab import drive\n",
    "drive.mount('/content/drive')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
